msgctxt "CompareContinuousDistributions|"
msgid ""
"Obtain the p-value of the goodness-of-fit tests using parametric bootstrap. "
"In this case, the test statistics are always Kolmorogov-Smirnov, and Cramér–"
"von Mises and Anderson-Darling for simple null hypothesis."
msgstr ""

